-- Purpose: Handles receiving, accepting, and declining incoming car gifts from other players.
-- Runs on: Client
-- Location: StarterPlayerScripts
-- Dependencies: Players, ReplicatedStorage, TweenService, Debris
-- Public API: N/A
-- Networking: Listens to 'IncomingGift' & 'GiftResult'. Fires 'ResolveGift'.
-- Security: Sanitizes user input for RichText. Validates connection teardown to prevent exploits.
-- Performance: Optimized Tween cancelation and task.delay management to prevent memory leaks.
-- Notes: Incorporates specific Sender and Receiver Notification displays based on cross-referenced ReplicatedStorage modules.

